
'''''Kimberley Jim''''' ni filime yo gusetsa y'umuziki yo muri [[Afrika]] y'epfo yasohotse 1963 yayobowe na Emil Nofal ikinwamo Jim Reeves, Madeleine Usher na Clive Parnell . <ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20090522045238/http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/title/65287 BFI.org]</ref> Umugambi wayo ukurikira umuririmbyi [[Amerika|w'umunyamerika]] witabira kwihuta kwa diyama ya Kimberley muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo mu mpera zikinyejana cya 19. By'umwihariko, "Jim Reeves na Clive Parnell bakina abantu bakundwa na con-men binjiza amafaranga yo kugurisha imiti y’ipatanti no gushuka kuri poker ... babiri bashora amafaranga yabo mu guteza imbere ikirombe cya diyama ariko bagomba kurenza umucuruzi waho ugoramye", nk'ukoincamake ibivuga. <ref>[https://www.thevideobeat.com/mod-movies/kimberley-jim-1963.html KIMBERLEY JIM 1963]</ref> <ref>[https://vimeo.com/ondemand/kimberleyjim KIMBERLEY JIM Trailer]</ref>

Reeves, umuririmbyi wo mu gihugu, yakunzwe cyane mu myaka ya za 1960. Nk’uko ikinyamakuru Billboard kibitangaza ngo " Reeves yamuritse mu mahanga mu [[Bwongereza]], [[Ubuhinde]], [[Ubudage]], ndetse no muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo". <ref>[https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6205510/a-tribute-to-country-crooner-jim-reeves-on-the-50th-anniversary-of-his-death A Tribute to Country Crooner Jim Reeves on the 50th Anniversary of His Death]</ref> Muri film, umuhanzi aririmba igice cy'indirimbo imwe muri Afrikaans. <ref>[http://www.mimosafilms.co.za/Archive/Film/65/kimberley-jim Kimberley Jim]</ref> Amajwi y'indirimbo 14 yarimo indirimbo "Kimberley Jim," "Strike It Rich," "Nakuze," "Ubuzima bwanjye ni Gypsy," "Navutse Kugira Amahirwe," "Rag Fashioned Rag," "Diamonds The Umusenyi, "" Inshuti Y'umunyamahanga Gusa, "" Gwa kandi Ukurikire, "" Umukinnyi ukina urusimbi "na" Dolly hamwe n'amavi yataye. " <ref>[https://www.thevideobeat.com/mod-movies/kimberley-jim-1963.html KIMBERLEY JIM 1963]</ref> <ref>[https://www.discogs.com/Jim-Reeves-Music-From-The-Movie-Kimberley-Jim/release/12752989 Jim Reeves – Music From The Movie "Kimberley Jim"]</ref>

Inyuma nyinshi zafatiwe amashusho mu gace ko mu mujyi muto [[Ubwongereza|w’Ubwongereza]] mu gihe imbere yafatiwe kuri sitidiyo ya Jamie Uys mu majyaruguru y’umugi wa Johannesburg . Nyuma Reeves yavuze ko yishimiye uburambe bwo gukora firime kandi ko azatekereza gukoresha byinshi mu mwuga we .  Iyi filime yasohotse mu 1965 nyuma y'urupfu rwa Reeves azize impanuka y'indege. <ref>[https://books.google.ca/books?id=AUAnDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA258&lpg=PA258&dq=film+kimberley+jim+set+in+diamond+rush&source=bl&ots=-_7uTazIqg&sig=ACfU3U25rz96NANOpR-RJzd6y1tkvcihCg&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjk37L9_4HqAhU8knIEHZ2hB2AQ6AEwA3oECAkQAQ#v=onepage&q=film%20kimberley%20jim%20set%20in%20diamond%20rush&f=false Changing Times: Music and Politics in 1964 page 258]</ref>

